quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif, Laam, Ra. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo n’Imana yonyene gusa). Aya majambo ari muri iki gitabu akoranije ibintu bikenewe vyose, nukuvyerekana neza k’umugaragaro"
  15,2,Kenshi na kenshi bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri bazokwipfuza iyo bobaye aba Isilamu
  15,3,"Nimubareke bafungure kandi binezereze hanyuma bahendwe n’icizero c’ububeshi, mugabo ubu vuba bazotahura"
  15,4,Natwe ntitwahoneje igisagara icarico cose atari uko ico gisagara ikiringo caco categekanijwe
  15,5,"Abantu abaribo bose ntibashobora kuba imbere y’isanganya ryabo, canke ntibashobora guteba mugihe umwanya wabo wageze"
  15,6,"Baravuze bati:- ewe wamanuriwe ubutumwa, mu vy’ukuri wewe uri umusazi"
  15,7,"Mbega\tni\tkuki\tutatuzanira\tabo\tbamarayika\tbokuduhonya\tniyaba\tari mubantu bavugisha ukuri"
  15,8,"Twebwe ntitumanura Abamarayika atari k’ukuri, aho rero ntibazohabwa ikiringo"
  15,9,Mu vy’ukuri nitwebwe twamanuye ubu butumwa ariyo Qur’ani nyeranda kandi mu vy’ukuri nitwebwe tuzoyakingira
  15,10,"Ntankeka\ttwarazanye\tintumwa\tz’Imana\timbere\tyabo\tiri\tmumirwi y’abantu bari imbere"
  15,11,"Kandi\tntibashikiwe\tn’intumwa\ty’Imana\tiyariyo\tyose\tatari\tuko bayikengereye"
  15,12,Ni nk’uku twinjiza mumitima yaba bahakanyi b’Imana
  15,13,Ntibemera ibi vyose mugihe yaho bahitiwe n’uburorero bw’abantu baho hambere yabo
  15,14,Iyo tubugurira abo bahakanyi b’Imana umuryango w’ijuru bakaguma baduga
  15,15,"Rero bari kuvuga bati:- amaso yacu yarozwe, ahubwo twebwe turi mu bantu barozwe"
  15,16,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwashize\tmw’Ijuru\tibituro\tnugushariza\tkubera\tabantu baziraba"
  15,17,Tukaba tuzikingiye n’amashetani aguma yirukanwa
  15,18,"Mugabo\tuwumviriza\tinkuru\tmunzira\tz’ubusuma,\trero\taca\takurikirwa n’igishirira c’umukomezwa kiboneka neza"
  15,19,N’Isi twarayishashe no muriyo tuyishira mwo imisozi nuku nagishamwo ibintu vyose kurugero rwaco
  15,20,Twaraba giriye muriyo ibintu vy’ubuzima bwanyu nivy’ubuzima bwabarya mutunze mwebwe ataco mubaha kubijanye n’imigisha
  15,21,"Ntakintu nakimwe atari uko amamuko yaco ava muri twebwe, kandi ntitukimanura atari kurugero rukwiye"
  15,22,"Kandi tuzana imiyaga yuzuye mwo urume nukumanura amazi y’imvura avuye muri ivyo bicu, hanyuma tukaba nywesha kuriyo kandi si mwebwe muyashiraho"
  15,23,"Ni twebwe turema kandi tukica, natwe ni twebwe basirwa"
  15,24,Kandi turabazi abatangura muri mwebwe kandi turabazi abacererwa
  15,25,"Ntankeka Umuremyi wawe niwe azobegeranya, mu vy’ukuri niyo nyene ubuhizi n’ubumenyi buhagije"
  15,26,"Twararemye ikiremwa muntu tumukuye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise n’ijwi, rivuye muvyondo vyirabura vyavunditswe"
  15,27,"N’ibisigo twabiremye imbere yaho, mu muriro w’umuyaga w’ubushuhe bwinshi cane"
  15,28,"N’Umuremyi wawe igihe yabwira Abamarayika biwe ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzorema umuntu ndamukuye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise ijwi rivuye muvyondo vyirabura bivunditswe"
  15,29,"Ninaheza kumurema nukumuhuheramwo umutima uvuye iwanje, rero nimu murweko nukumu gamburukira"
  15,30,Rero abamarayika bose hamwe bara gamburuka
  15,31,Dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi niwe yanse kuba hamwe naba gamburutse
  15,32,"Imana yavuze iti:- ewe Ibilisi vyabaye gute kutabaye hamwe naba gamburutse"
  15,33,"Shetani imwishura iti:- jewe sinshobora kugamburukira umuntu waremye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise ijwi rivuye muvyondo bivunze"
  15,34,"Imana ivuga iti:- nuve ngaho mugihe wirukanywe nukuba kure y’imigisha yose"
  15,35,Kandi mu vy’ukuri bizoba kuri wewe harimwo umuvumo kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka
  15,36,"Shetani yishura iti:- Muremyi wanje numpe umwanya kugeza k’umusi bazozurwa abantu bose"
  15,37,"Imana yishura iti:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubaronse ikibanza"
  15,38,Kugeza k’umusi w’umwanya wagenewe ushitse niho uzosandaba
  15,39,"Nayo yishura iti:- Muremyi wanje kubera yuko wanciriye urubanza rw’ukuzimira, nanje nzobaryosha ryosha aba bantu kuri iy’Isi nze ndabazimize bose"
  15,40,Dukuyemwo abantu bawe beranda bisukuye neza naneza
  15,41,"Imana ivuga iti:- iyi nzira yabo niyukuza iwanje kandi igororotse"
  15,42,"Mu vy’ukuri abantu banje, wewe ntabushobozi uzoba ufise kuribo, atari bamwe bagukurikira muri abo bazimiye"
  15,43,Kandi ntankeka umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu nibwo bwicaro bwabo bemerewe bose
  15,44,"Uwo muriro ufise imiryango indwi, no kumuryango umw’umwe hariho ahantu hagabuwe"
  15,45,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tabatinya\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tbazoba\tbari\tmumirima n’amasoko y’amazi y’umusarara"
  15,46,Nimuyinjiremwo n’amahoro ntangere
  15,47,"Kandi\ttuzokuramwo\tamafundo\tyari\tmubikiriza\tvyabo,\tkandi\tbazoba abavandimwe bakundana bicaye hejuru y’inyegano zacami barabana"
  15,48,"Ntibazo korwako n’ingorane, canke ngo bakurwemwo"
  15,49,Babwire abantu banje yuko jewe mfise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije